sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Caller
    participant G as AXME Cloud Gateway
    participant I as Identity Validator
    participant Z as Authorization Engine
    participant A as Audit/Trace

    C->>G: API request
    G->>I: validate machine key (x-api-key / AXME_API_KEY)
    alt x-api-key invalid or missing
        I-->>G: reject
        G-->>C: 401 missing_platform_api_key / invalid_platform_api_key
    else x-api-key valid
        I-->>G: ok
        G->>I: validate actor token (if required on route)
        alt actor token invalid/missing/scope mismatch
            I-->>G: reject
            G-->>C: 401/403 missing_actor_token / invalid_actor_scope
        else identity context valid
            G->>Z: enforce owner scope + role/grants
            alt unauthorized
                Z-->>G: deny
                G-->>C: 403 forbidden
            else authorized
                Z-->>G: allow
                G->>A: record audit + trace metadata
                G-->>C: execute and return response
            end
        end
    end
